quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  2,47,Oh Bantwana bakwa-Israyeli! Khumbulani ububele bami enganenzela bona nganikhetha ngaphezu kwabanye emihlabeni
  2,48,"Futhi sabani usuku lapho umphefumulo ungeke usizwe omunye umphefumulo ngalutho nokuzincengela angeke kwamukelwe, angeke kuthathwe inhlawulo kuwo futhi angeke basizwe"
  2,49,Futhi (khumbulani) ngesikhathi sinivikela kubantu bakaFaro benethwesa isijeziso esinzima bebulala amadodana enu beshiya abesifazane bephila futhi lokho kwangukulingwa kwenu okukhulu okuvela eNkosini yenu
  2,50,Futhi (khumbulani) sanihlukanisela ulwandle sanihlenga sabe sesiminzisa abantu bakaFaro kulapho nibhekile
  2,51,Futhi khumbulani ngesikhathi senza isethembiso noMozisi ubusuku obungamashumi amane emva kwakhe nasala nathatha ithole (nalikhonza laba yisithixo senu) naba ngabenzi bokubi
  2,52,Sabe sesiyanixolela emva kwalokho ukuze nikhombise ukubonga
  2,53,Futhi (khumbulani ngesikhathi) sinika uMose incwadi nokunehlukanisela ukuze niholwe
  2,54,"Futhi (khumbulani) ngesikhathi uMose ethi kubantu bakhe, “Oh Bantu bami! Nenze okubi emiphefumulweni yenu ngokuthatha ithole (ukuba nilikhonze) ngakho-ke buyelani kumdali wenu ngentethelelo, nizibulale nina uqobo lokho kungcono kunina emehlweni omdali wenu wabe eseyanithethelela ngempela ungothethelelayo onesihawu”"
  2,55,Futhi (khumbulani) ngesikhathi nithi “Oh! Mose! Angeke sikukholwe ngaphandle kokuba sizibonele uMvelinqangi uqobo lwethu” nabe senithathwa umbani kulapho nibhekile
  2,56,Sabe sesiyanivusa emuva kokufa kwenu ukuze nibe nokubonga
  2,57,"Sawenza amafu ukuba abeyithunzi phezu kwenu, sathumela kunina imana nezigwaca, yidlani ezintweni ezinhle esiniphe zona, abazange basone ngalutho kodwa bona imiphefumulo yabo"
  2,58,"Futhi khumbulani ukuthi sathi, ngenani kulelidolobha nidle okukulo noma ngabe yini ngendlela enithanda ngayo ningene esangweni niguqile ngokuzithoba nithi, “sithethelele” siyonithethelela izono zenu futhi siyobandisa abenzi bokuhle"
  2,59,Kodwa labo ababengalungile baguqula inkulumo hayi leyo eyayishiwo kubona sabe sesehlisela kulabo abonayo isijeziso esivela ezulwini